FOLDER.NAME: EDWTD_REV_MEASURE
FOLDER.DESCRIPTION: This folder will have all the informatica objects related GL and INV REVENUE MEASURE table load process for rel3.0 Approvers:Kathy Kwong, Murali Marni, Geetha Bhakta

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT GL.REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY ,GL.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT ,GL.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD ,GL.XCAT_FLG AS XCAT_FLG ,GL.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,GL.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,GL.ELA_FLG ,GL.XCAT_FLG AS NEW_XCAT_FLG ,OMAP.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME AS NEW_BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,OMAP.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG AS NEW_RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,CASE WHEN NEW_XCAT_FLG='Y' THEN 'Y' ELSE OMAP.ELA_FLG END AS NEW_ELA_FLG FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE GL INNER JOIN $$COMREFVWDB.R_FISCAL_MONTH_TO_YEAR RFMY ON GL.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT = RFMY.FISCAL_YEAR_MONTH_INT INNER JOIN $$COMREFVWDB.MT_OFFER_TYPE_PRDT_MAP OMAP ON GL.PRODUCT_KEY = OMAP.PRODUCT_KEY AND GL.DV_PRODUCT_KEY= OMAP.DV_PRODUCT_KEY AND GL.DV_ATTRIBUTION_CD = OMAP.BK_OFFER_ATTRBTN_TYPE_CD WHERE /* GL.DD_BK_DIRECT_CORP_ADJ_TYPE_CD ='POS ALLOCATION' */ /* COMMENTED AS PART OF MAY21ST REL */ GL.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD IN ('POS') AND RFMY.FISCAL_YEAR_AGE BETWEEN 0 AND 3 AND RFMY.FISCAL_MONTH_AGE >= 0 AND OMAP.EDW_UPDATE_DTM >( SELECT LAST_EXTRACT_DATE FROM $$ETLVWDB.CTL_ETL_LAST_EXTRACT_DATES WHERE JOB_STREAM_ID='wf_WI_INV_REV_END_CST_RTR_POS_SMR' AND TABLE_NAME ='WI_INV_RTR_MAP_FLG_POS_SMR') AND ( GL.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME <>OMAP.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME OR GL.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG <> OMAP.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG OR GL.ELA_FLG <> (CASE WHEN NEW_XCAT_FLG='Y' THEN 'Y' ELSE OMAP.ELA_FLG END ) ) AND 1=2

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY ,DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT ,REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD ,GL.XCAT_FLG ,GL.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,GL.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,GL.ELA_FLG /* ,NSO.XCAT_FLG AS NEW_XCAT_FLG */ ,(CASE WHEN NSO.XCAT_FLG = 'Y' THEN NSO.XCAT_FLG ELSE NP.XCAT_FLG END) AS NEW_XCAT_FLG/* added as part of april9th2017 */ ,GL.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME AS NEW_BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME /* added as part of april9th2017 */ ,GL.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG AS NEW_RECURRING_OFFER_FLG /* added as part of april9th2017 */ ,GL.ELA_FLG AS NEW_ELA_FLG /* added as part of april9th2017 */ ,'Y' AS XCAT_FLG_UPD ,'N' AS MAP_FLGS_UPD FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE GL INNER JOIN $$COMREFVWDB.R_FISCAL_MONTH_TO_YEAR RFMY ON GL.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT = RFMY.FISCAL_YEAR_MONTH_INT INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_SALES_ORDER_TV NSO ON GL.SALES_ORDER_KEY = NSO.SALES_ORDER_KEY INNER JOIN (SELECT ITEM_KEY,XCAT_FLG,EDW_UPDATE_DATETIME FROM $$COMREFVWDB.N_PRODUCT ) NP ON GL.PRODUCT_KEY=NP.ITEM_KEY WHERE NSO.END_TV_DATETIME = '3500-01-01 00:00:00' /* AND GL.DD_BK_DIRECT_CORP_ADJ_TYPE_CD ='POS ALLOCATION' */ /* COMMENTED AS PART OF MAY21ST REL */ AND GL.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD IN ('POS') AND RFMY.FISCAL_YEAR_AGE BETWEEN 0 AND 3 AND RFMY.FISCAL_MONTH_AGE >= 0 AND NSO.EDW_UPDATE_DATETIME >( SELECT LAST_EXTRACT_DATE FROM $$ETLVWDB.CTL_ETL_LAST_EXTRACT_DATES WHERE JOB_STREAM_ID='wf_WI_INV_REV_END_CST_RTR_POS_SMR' AND TABLE_NAME ='WI_INV_RTR_XCATMAP_FLG_POS_SMR' ) AND GL.XCAT_FLG <> (CASE WHEN NSO.XCAT_FLG = 'Y' THEN NSO.XCAT_FLG ELSE NP.XCAT_FLG END) AND 1=2
UNION SELECT REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY ,DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT ,REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD ,GL.XCAT_FLG ,GL.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,GL.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,GL.ELA_FLG /* ,NP.XCAT_FLG AS NEW_XCAT_FLG */ ,(CASE WHEN NSO.XCAT_FLG = 'Y' THEN NSO.XCAT_FLG ELSE NP.XCAT_FLG END) AS NEW_XCAT_FLG/* added as part of april9th2017 */ ,GL.BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME AS NEW_BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,GL.RECURRING_OFFER_FLG AS NEW_RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,GL.ELA_FLG AS NEW_ELA_FLG ,'Y' AS XCAT_FLG_UPD ,'N' AS MAP_FLGS_UPD FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE GL INNER JOIN $$COMREFVWDB.R_FISCAL_MONTH_TO_YEAR RFMY ON GL.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT = RFMY.FISCAL_YEAR_MONTH_INT INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_SALES_ORDER_TV NSO ON GL.SALES_ORDER_KEY = NSO.SALES_ORDER_KEY INNER JOIN (SELECT ITEM_KEY,XCAT_FLG,EDW_UPDATE_DATETIME FROM $$COMREFVWDB.N_PRODUCT ) NP ON GL.PRODUCT_KEY=NP.ITEM_KEY WHERE NSO.END_TV_DATETIME = '3500-01-01 00:00:00' /*AND GL.DD_BK_DIRECT_CORP_ADJ_TYPE_CD ='POS ALLOCATION' */ /* COMMENTED AS PART OF MAY21ST REL */ AND GL.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD IN ('POS') AND RFMY.FISCAL_YEAR_AGE BETWEEN 0 AND 3 AND RFMY.FISCAL_MONTH_AGE >= 0 AND NP.EDW_UPDATE_DATETIME >( SELECT LAST_EXTRACT_DATE FROM $$ETLVWDB.CTL_ETL_LAST_EXTRACT_DATES WHERE JOB_STREAM_ID='wf_WI_INV_REV_END_CST_RTR_POS_SMR' AND TABLE_NAME ='WI_INV_RTR_XCATMAP_FLG_POS_SMR') AND GL.XCAT_FLG <> (CASE WHEN NSO.XCAT_FLG = 'Y' THEN NSO.XCAT_FLG ELSE NP.XCAT_FLG END) AND 1=2

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY ,DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT ,REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD ,XCAT_FLG ,BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,ELA_FLG ,NEW_XCAT_FLG ,NEW_BK_OFFER_TYPE_NAME ,NEW_RECURRING_OFFER_FLG ,NEW_ELA_FLG ,'N' AS XCAT_FLG_UPD ,'Y' AS MAP_FLGS_UPD FROM $$STGDB.WI_INV_RTR_MAP_FLG_POS_SMR MAPFLG WHERE NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM $$STGDB.WI_INV_RTR_XCATMAP_FLG_POS_SMR CMN WHERE CMN.REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY = MAPFLG.REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY AND CMN.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT = MAPFLG.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT AND CMN.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD = MAPFLG.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD )
